properties.Name: Del Rey Landing Fuel Dock
properties.hours:
Open seven days a week, as follows:
Summer: 7AM to 6PM
Winter: 7AM to 5PM
properties.description:
Del Rey Landing

The fuel dock is located on the west side of the Main Channel at the entrance of "A" basin.

The Del Rey Landing offers fuel and a convenience store that sells food, boating accessories, lottery tickets, live bait and fishing gear.

Transient docks are available for temporary dinghy tie-up, along with slips for mega-yachts.
